### 👥 READ - Get All Users (including active only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 🔍 READ - Get User by ID (replace :id with actual user ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### ✏ UPDATE - Update User by ID (replace :id with actual user ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "age": 26,
  "city": "Boston"
}

### ✏ UPDATE - Partial Update User Email
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane.updated@example.com"
}

### 🗑 DELETE - Soft Delete User by ID (replace :id with actual user ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### 👥 READ - Get All Users Again (should not show soft deleted users)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 🔍 READ - Try to Get Soft Deleted User (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### 🗑 DELETE - Soft Delete Another User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/2

### 👥 READ - Final Users List
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### ❌ UPDATE - Try to Update Soft Deleted User (should fail)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "This should fail"
}

